        {
            "definition": {
                "background_color": "white",
                "content": "## Custom Metrics Billing\n\nClick [HERE](https://docs.datadoghq.com/account_management/billing/custom_metrics/?tab=countrategauge)\n\n**Note**: To identify the biggest contributors to your custom metric count, check the bottom of your usage page.\n\n## Ways to reduce count/things to check\n\n1. Is this metric being using anywhere (dashboard or monitor)? Ask DD for the unused custom metric report.\n2. Could this be a service check instead of a metric? The name and value suggest it's just a status (0 or 1) so perhaps could be better suited as a check;\n3. Remove or lower cardinality of tags where possible\n4. Is another DD feature providing similar metrics?\n5. Should this be an integration with standard metrics?\n6. Is this a histogram or distribution, which increases count by 5x. [More](https://docs.datadoghq.com/account_management/billing/custom_metrics/?tab=histogram)\n7. Remove host level granularity\n8. Metrics Without Limits beta. Click [HERE](https://www.datadoghq.com/videos/introducing-metrics-without-limits/)\n9. Distribution metrics. Click [HERE](https://docs.datadoghq.com/metrics/distributions/#customize-tagging)",
                "font_size": "14",
                "show_tick": false,
                "text_align": "left",
                "tick_edge": "left",
